, D. D. Using correspondence analysis to monitor the persona segmentation process. In NordiCHI'12 (2012), 265--274.  <span class=\"references__pub-id doi\"></span><span class=\"references__suffix\"><a class=\"google-scholar\" href=\"http://scholar.google.com/scholar?hl=en&q=Laporte%2C+L.%2C+Slegers%2C+K.%2C+and+Grooff%2C+D.+D.+Using+correspondence+analysis+to+monitor+the+persona+segmentation+process.+In+NordiCHI%2712+%282012%29%2C+265%2D%2D274.+10.1145%2F2399016.2399058+\"target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"visibility-hidden\">Google Scholar</span><img src=\"/specs/products/acm/images/googleScholar.svg\" class=\"simple-tooltip__block--b\" alt=\"Google Scholar\"/></a></span><span class=\"references__suffix\"><a href=\"/doi/10.1145/2399016.2399058\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"visibility-hidden\">Digital Library</span><img class=\"simple-tooltip__block--b\" data-title=\"Digital Library\" alt=\"Digital Library\" src=\"/templates/jsp/_ux3/_acm/images/DL_icon.svg\"></img></a></span></span></li><li id=\"ref-00026\" class=\"&#xA;                references__item&#xA;            \"><span class=\"references__note\">Larson, R., and Csikszentmihalyi, M. The Experience Sampling Method. New Directions for Methodology of Social and Behavioral Science 15 (1983), 41--56.<span class=\"references__suffix\"><a class=\"google-scholar\" href=\"http://scholar.google.com/scholar?hl=en&q=Larson%2C+R.%2C+and+Csikszentmihalyi%2C+M.+The+Experience+Sampling+Method.+New+Directions+for+Methodology+of+Social+and+Behavioral+Science+15+%281983%29%2C+41%2D%2D56.\"target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"visibility-hidden\">Google Scholar</span><img src=\"/specs/products/acm/images/googleScholar.svg\" class=\"simple-tooltip__block--b\" alt=\"Google Scholar\"/></a></span></span></li><li id=\"ref-00027\" class=\"&#xA;                references__item&#xA;            \"><span class=\"references__note\">Lieberman, H., Paterno, F., and Wulf, V., Eds. End-User Development. Kluwer/ Springer, 2006.<span class=\"referen